                     <interp inst="t17990403-24-person263" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am an officer, I took charge of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>The prisoner left his defence to his Counsel, and called one witness, who had known him eleven years, and gave him an excellent character.</p>
